
Greenstar Janitorial offers Environmental Organizations environmentally friendly Housekeeping cleaning services in Davis and Yolo County the surrounding areas.

They do houses and businesses, with a goal to to help you maintain a very clean living and/or work space while reducing your carbon footprint and eliminating pollutants.

As the trend in cleaning products moves increasingly towards disposables the environmental impact of household cleaning is also mounting. At Greenstar Janitorial they use Green Seal approved best practices to decrease pollutants and energy use while keeping your home or business healthy and clean. They are dedicated to encouraging and enabling our customers to make educated, environmentally conscious and cost effective choices. Just as the choices we make about what we eat affect our health and the planets health so do the choices we make about what cleaning products and methods we use.


